  <brief_title>Efficacy Study of Oral Sapacitabine to Treat Acute Myeloid Leukemia in Elderly Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase 2 Study of Oral Sapacitabine in Elderly Patients With Acute Myeloid Leukemia Previously Untreated or in First Relapse, or Previously Treated Myelodysplastic Syndromes</official_title>
